# Local file-mode runtime state (views, board prefs, DB-native items, hierarchy,
# releases, ...): per-user scratch data, never sample data. config.yml is the one
# tracked file in here. A glob so new local-*.json siblings are covered too.
.specboards/local-*.json
.claude/worktrees/
